title: BRAND NEW CHERRY FLAVOR Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment:
Edited this video drinking a delicious 🍒 coke! What did ya'll think of Brand New Cherry Flavor?

Check out my other Horror videos here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7i5oOjx21bz-hnkmbeCmU4j
The narrative was actually very simple but creatively blurred, Boro set the whole thing up so she can feed on Lisa who has the blood of a mystic.
another funny thing about lou getting blinded is that he’ll never be able to watch another movie again

This show caught me by surprise and a good way.   Lately, all Netflix shows have started to feel formulaic but this show breaks from it. 

   Its suspsenful, its dark and crude humor works and the mysticism and magic influence of Brazilian folklore really adds a whole other layer to the series

I mean, anytime you get Catherine Keener, it's gonna be wild! She's fantastic! I enjoyed the hell out of this show! It was like a mix of Cronenberg and Lynch and it worked quite well. I hope there is more!
